Package gameoflife

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileIO
    Main class that operates the importing and exporting of game board configurations.
    GameBoardCell
    The "Grid" of click-able buttons on the visual program.
    GameBoardController
    The functions and inner workings of the GUI.
    GameBoardModel
    The "Model" file that displays all the GUI elements.
    GameBoardTile
    PseudoClass is used for the Pseudo properties of the buttons.
    GameOfLife
    The main .java file that runs all the other java,fxml and css files.
    GameSpeedControl
    Constructor for setting the maximum, minimum and current tick time.
    Sound
    The Sound class provides support for sound in the game.
